<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>EqualCity — SAIRAM 17 IN 7</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;700;800&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0d0d0f;
    --panel: #16161a;
    --border: #2a2a35;
    --accent1: #f6c90e;
    --accent2: #ff5c5c;
    --accent3: #4af0a2;
    --accent4: #7b9cff;
    --sdg10: #dd1367;
    --sdg11: #fd9d24;
    --text: #e8e8f0;
    --muted: #6b6b80;
  }
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }
  body::before {
    content:'';
    position:fixed; inset:0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(246,201,14,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(246,201,14,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 48px 48px;
    pointer-events:none; z-index:0;
  }
  .screen { display:none; position:relative; z-index:1; }
  .screen.active { display:block; }

  /* ── COLLEGE HEADER BAR ── */
  .college-bar {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1628 0%, #0f2040 100%);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent1);
    padding: .65rem 1.2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .9rem;
    position: relative; z-index: 10;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .college-logo-wrap {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    display:flex; align-items:center;
    flex-shrink:0;
    min-width: 90px;
  }
  .college-logo-wrap img {
    height: 42px;
    width: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
  .college-logo-fallback {
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
    font-weight:800; font-size:.75rem;
    color:#002366; line-height:1.2;
    text-align:center;
    padding: 2px 4px;
  }
  .college-info { flex:1; min-width:160px; }
  .college-name {
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
    font-size:.78rem; font-weight:800;
    color:#fff; line-height:1.3;
  }
  .college-sub {
    font-size:.57rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);
    letter-spacing:.05em;
  }
  .sdg-strip {
    display:flex; gap:.5rem; align-items:center;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .sdg-pill {
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:.35rem;
    border-radius:3px; padding:.28rem .6rem;
    font-size:.58rem; font-weight:700;
    letter-spacing:.05em; text-transform:uppercase;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:transform .15s, filter .15s;
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .sdg-pill:hover { transform:scale(1.05); filter:brightness(1.15); }
  .sdg-pill.sdg10 { background:var(--sdg10); color:#fff; }
  .sdg-pill.sdg11 { background:var(--sdg11); color:#000; }
  .sdg-pill .sdg-num { font-size:.8rem; font-weight:800; }
  .sairam-badge {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent1), #ff9500);
    color: #000;
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
    font-weight:800; font-size:.68rem;
    letter-spacing:.08em;
    padding:.38rem .85rem;
    border-radius:3px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    white-space:nowrap;
    animation: badgePulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes badgePulse {
    0%,100%{ box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(246,201,14,.45); }
    50%{ box-shadow:0 0 0 8px rgba(246,201,14,0); }
  }

  /* ── SDG MODAL ── */
  .sdg-modal-overlay {
    display:none; position:fixed; inset:0;
    background:rgba(0,0,0,.78); z-index:1000;
    align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    padding:1rem;
  }
  .sdg-modal-overlay.show { display:flex; }
  .sdg-modal {
    background:var(--panel);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:8px;
    max-width:480px; width:100%;
    padding:1.4rem;
    animation:fadeUp .25s ease;
  }
  .sdg-modal-header {
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:.9rem;
    margin-bottom:.9rem;
  }
  .sdg-icon-big {
    width:62px; height:62px; border-radius:8px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight:800;
    font-size:1rem; flex-shrink:0; line-height:1.15;
    text-align:center; white-space:pre;
  }
  .sdg-icon-big.sdg10 { background:var(--sdg10); color:#fff; }
  .sdg-icon-big.sdg11 { background:var(--sdg11); color:#000; }
  .sdg-modal h2 { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size:.95rem; font-weight:800; }
  .sdg-modal-label { font-size:.58rem; color:var(--muted); letter-spacing:.12em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:.3rem; }
  .sdg-modal-body { font-size:.73rem; line-height:1.8; color:var(--muted); }
  .sdg-modal-body strong { color:var(--text); }
  .sdg-targets { margin-top:.75rem; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:.35rem; }
  .sdg-target {
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
    border-radius:3px; padding:.45rem .65rem;
    font-size:.68rem; line-height:1.6;
  }
  .btn-close-modal {
    margin-top:1.1rem; width:100%;
    background:transparent; border:1px solid var(--border);
    color:var(--text); padding:.55rem;
    cursor:pointer; font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;
    font-size:.72rem; border-radius:3px;
    transition:background .2s;
  }
  .btn-close-modal:hover { background:var(--border); }

  /* ═══════════════ TITLE SCREEN ═══════════════ */
  #title-screen {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 68px);
    display:flex; flex-direction:column;
    align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    padding:2rem; text-align:center;
  }
  #title-screen.active { display:flex; }
  .logo-badge {
    display:inline-block;
    border:2px solid var(--accent1);
    color:var(--accent1);
    font-size:.6rem; letter-spacing:.22em;
    padding:.28rem .85rem; margin-bottom:.7rem;
    text-transform:uppercase;
  }
  .sdg-badges-title {
    display:flex; gap:.5rem; justify-content:center;
    margin-bottom:1.1rem; flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  h1.game-title {
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
    font-size:clamp(2.8rem,8vw,6rem);
    font-weight:800; line-height:1;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent1) 0%, var(--accent3) 60%, var(--accent4) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip:text; -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
    margin-bottom:.5rem;
    animation: titlePulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes titlePulse {
    0%,100%{ filter:brightness(1); }
    50%{ filter:brightness(1.2); }
  }
  .game-subtitle { color:var(--muted); font-size:.8rem; letter-spacing:.1em; margin-bottom:.4rem; }
  .sdg-tagline {
    font-size:.68rem; letter-spacing:.05em;
    margin-bottom:2.2rem;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:.45rem;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .sdg-tagline .t10 { color:var(--sdg10); font-weight:700; }
  .sdg-tagline .t11 { color:var(--sdg11); font-weight:700; }
  .sdg-tagline .sep { color:var(--border); }
  .concept-cards {
    display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.9rem;
    justify-content:center; max-width:760px;
    margin-bottom:2.2rem;
  }
  .concept-card {
    background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:4px; padding:.9rem 1.1rem;
    max-width:208px; text-align:left;
    position:relative; overflow:hidden;
    transition: transform .2s, border-color .2s;
  }
  .concept-card:hover { transform:translateY(-3px); border-color:var(--accent1); }
  .concept-card::before {
    content:attr(data-num);
    position:absolute; top:-.2rem; right:.5rem;
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size:3.5rem; font-weight:800;
    color:rgba(246,201,14,.07); line-height:1;
  }
  .concept-card h3 {
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size:.72rem;
    color:var(--accent1); margin-bottom:.35rem;
    text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.08em;
  }
  .concept-card p { font-size:.66rem; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.6; }
  .concept-card .sdg-tag {
    display:inline-block; font-size:.56rem;
    padding:.12rem .38rem; border-radius:2px;
    margin-top:.45rem; font-weight:700;
  }
  .concept-card .sdg-tag.s10 { background:var(--sdg10); color:#fff; }
  .concept-card .sdg-tag.s11 { background:var(--sdg11); color:#000; }
  .btn-primary {
    background:var(--accent1); color:#000;
    border:none; cursor:pointer;
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:1rem;
    letter-spacing:.1em; padding:.9rem 3rem;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0% 100%);
    transition: background .2s, transform .15s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background:#ffe040; transform:scale(1.03); }

  /* ═══════════════ GAME SCREEN ═══════════════ */
  #game-screen { padding:1.4rem; max-width:920px; margin:0 auto; }
  #game-screen.active { display:block; }
  .hud {
    display:flex; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;
    gap:.7rem; margin-bottom:1.1rem;
    padding-bottom:.9rem;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .hud-title { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight:800; font-size:.95rem; color:var(--accent1); margin-right:auto; }
  .hud-sdg { display:flex; gap:.35rem; }
  .hud-sdg-dot {
    width:28px; height:28px; border-radius:3px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-size:.52rem; font-weight:800; line-height:1.1;
    text-align:center; cursor:pointer;
    transition:transform .15s; white-space:pre;
  }
  .hud-sdg-dot:hover { transform:scale(1.1); }
  .hud-sdg-dot.s10 { background:var(--sdg10); color:#fff; }
  .hud-sdg-dot.s11 { background:var(--sdg11); color:#000; }
  .stat-pill {
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:.35rem;
    background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:2px; padding:.28rem .65rem; font-size:.66rem;
  }
  .stat-pill span { color:var(--accent3); font-weight:700; }
  .level-header { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size:1.35rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:.3rem; }
  .level-sub { font-size:.7rem; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:.7rem; line-height:1.7; }
  .level-sdg-link {
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:.45rem;
    margin-bottom:1.1rem; padding:.38rem .75rem;
    border-radius:3px; font-size:.64rem;
    font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.05em;
    border:1px solid transparent;
  }
  .level-sdg-link.s10 { background:rgba(221,19,103,.12); border-color:rgba(221,19,103,.3); color:var(--sdg10); }
  .level-sdg-link.s11 { background:rgba(253,157,36,.12); border-color:rgba(253,157,36,.3); color:var(--sdg11); }
  .level-sdg-link.both { background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(221,19,103,.1),rgba(253,157,36,.1)); border-color:rgba(246,201,14,.25); color:var(--accent1); }
  .scenario-box {
    background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-left:3px solid var(--accent4);
    border-radius:4px; padding:1.05rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom:1.2rem;
  }
  .scenario-box .tag { font-size:.57rem; color:var(--accent4); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.15em; margin-bottom:.45rem; }
  .scenario-box p { font-size:.78rem; line-height:1.75; }
  .choices { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:.65rem; margin-bottom:1.3rem; }
  .choice-btn {
    background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:4px; padding:.88rem 1.05rem;
    color:var(--text); cursor:pointer; text-align:left;
    font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:.74rem; line-height:1.6;
    transition: border-color .2s, background .2s, transform .15s;
    display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:.65rem;
  }
  .choice-btn:hover:not(:disabled) { border-color:var(--accent1); background:#1e1e26; transform:translateX(4px); }
  .choice-btn:disabled { opacity:.55; cursor:default; transform:none; }
  .choice-btn.correct { border-color:var(--accent3); background:rgba(74,240,162,.08); }
  .choice-btn.wrong   { border-color:var(--accent2); background:rgba(255,92,92,.08); }
  .choice-icon { font-size:1.05rem; flex-shrink:0; margin-top:.05rem; }
  .feedback-box {
    background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-left:3px solid var(--accent3); border-radius:4px;
    padding:.95rem 1.15rem; font-size:.75rem; line-height:1.75;
    margin-bottom:1.3rem; display:none;
  }
  .feedback-box.show { display:block; animation:fadeUp .3s ease; }
  .feedback-box.bad  { border-color:var(--accent2); }
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from{ opacity:0; transform:translateY(6px); }
    to  { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
  }
  .feedback-label { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:.7rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.1em; margin-bottom:.38rem; }
  .feedback-box.show .feedback-label { color:var(--accent3); }
  .feedback-box.bad  .feedback-label { color:var(--accent2); }
  .feedback-sdg {
    margin-top:.55rem; padding:.45rem .65rem;
    border-radius:3px; font-size:.66rem; font-style:italic; opacity:.9;
  }
  .feedback-sdg.s10 { background:rgba(221,19,103,.1); color:var(--sdg10); }
  .feedback-sdg.s11 { background:rgba(253,157,36,.1); color:var(--sdg11); }
  .feedback-sdg.both { background:rgba(246,201,14,.08); color:var(--accent1); }
  .level-progress { height:3px; background:var(--border); border-radius:2px; margin-bottom:1.3rem; overflow:hidden; }
  .level-progress-fill { height:100%; background:var(--accent1); border-radius:2px; transition:width .6s ease; }
  .action-bar { display:flex; gap:.75rem; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .btn-next {
    background:var(--accent3); color:#000; border:none; cursor:pointer;
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:.8rem;
    letter-spacing:.08em; padding:.68rem 1.9rem; text-transform:uppercase;
    clip-path: polygon(6px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 6px) 100%, 0% 100%);
    transition:background .2s, transform .15s; display:none;
  }
  .btn-next.show { display:inline-block; }
  .btn-next:hover { background:#6fffc0; transform:scale(1.03); }
  .mini-map { display:flex; gap:4px; margin-bottom:1.2rem; }
  .map-node { flex:1; height:6px; border-radius:2px; background:var(--border); transition:background .3s; }
  .map-node.done  { background:var(--accent3); }
  .map-node.active{ background:var(--accent1); }

  /* ═══════════════ END SCREEN ═══════════════ */
  #end-screen {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 68px);
    display:flex; flex-direction:column;
    align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    padding:2rem; text-align:center;
  }
  #end-screen.active { display:flex; }
  .end-score { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(3rem,10vw,7rem); font-weight:800; line-height:1; color:var(--accent1); margin-bottom:.5rem; }
  .end-label { font-size:.7rem; color:var(--muted); letter-spacing:.18em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:1.4rem; }
  .end-sdg-summary { display:flex; gap:.75rem; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:1.4rem; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .end-sdg-card { border-radius:6px; padding:.75rem 1.1rem; max-width:195px; text-align:left; }
  .end-sdg-card.s10 { background:rgba(221,19,103,.15); border:1px solid rgba(221,19,103,.35); }
  .end-sdg-card.s11 { background:rgba(253,157,36,.15); border:1px solid rgba(253,157,36,.35); }
  .end-sdg-card .sdg-title { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight:800; font-size:.72rem; margin-bottom:.28rem; }
  .end-sdg-card.s10 .sdg-title { color:var(--sdg10); }
  .end-sdg-card.s11 .sdg-title { color:var(--sdg11); }
  .end-sdg-card p { font-size:.65rem; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.6; }
  .end-verdict { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:.55rem; }
  .end-msg { font-size:.76rem; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.75; max-width:500px; margin-bottom:1.8rem; }
  .score-breakdown { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.75rem; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:1.6rem; }
  .score-item { background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:4px; padding:.65rem .95rem; font-size:.68rem; }
  .score-item .val { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--accent3); display:block; margin-bottom:.18rem; }
  .end-footer { font-size:.6rem; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:1.4rem; letter-spacing:.07em; line-height:1.8; }
  .end-footer strong { color:var(--accent1); }
  .btn-restart {
    background:transparent; border:1px solid var(--accent1);
    color:var(--accent1); font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight:700;
    font-size:.8rem; letter-spacing:.1em; padding:.68rem 2.1rem;
    cursor:pointer; text-transform:uppercase;
    transition:background .2s, color .2s;
  }
  .btn-restart:hover { background:var(--accent1); color:#000; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── COLLEGE HEADER ── -->
<div class="college-bar">
  <div class="college-logo-wrap" id="logo-wrap">
    <img src="https://sairam.edu.in/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sairam-sec-logo.png"
         alt="Sri Sairam Engineering College"
         style="height:42px;width:auto;"
         onerror="document.getElementById('logo-wrap').innerHTML='<div class=\'college-logo-fallback\'>SRI SAIRAM<br>ENG. COLLEGE</div>'">
  </div>
  <div class="college-info">
    <div class="college-name">Sri Sairam Engineering College, Chennai</div>
    <div class="college-sub">West Tambaram · Anna University Affiliated · NAAC A+ · NBA Accredited</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sdg-strip">
    <div class="sdg-pill sdg10" onclick="openSDG(10)">
      <span class="sdg-num">10</span> Reduced Inequalities
    </div>
    <div class="sdg-pill sdg11" onclick="openSDG(11)">
      <span class="sdg-num">11</span> Sustainable Cities
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="sairam-badge">SAIRAM 17 IN 7</div>
</div>

<!-- SDG Modal -->
<div class="sdg-modal-overlay" id="sdg-modal-overlay" onclick="closeSDGOverlay(event)">
  <div class="sdg-modal">
    <div class="sdg-modal-header">
      <div class="sdg-icon-big" id="sdg-icon-big"></div>
      <div>
        <div class="sdg-modal-label">UN Sustainable Development Goal</div>
        <h2 id="sdg-modal-title"></h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sdg-modal-body" id="sdg-modal-body"></div>
    <button class="btn-close-modal" onclick="document.getElementById('sdg-modal-overlay').classList.remove('show')">✕ Close</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════ TITLE SCREEN ═══════════════ -->
<div id="title-screen" class="screen active">
  <div class="logo-badge">SAIRAM 17 IN 7 · Day 5 · Game Mapping Challenge</div>
  <div class="sdg-badges-title">
    <div class="sdg-pill sdg10" onclick="openSDG(10)"><span class="sdg-num">SDG 10</span> Reduced Inequalities</div>
    <div class="sdg-pill sdg11" onclick="openSDG(11)"><span class="sdg-num">SDG 11</span> Sustainable Cities &amp; Communities</div>
  </div>
  <h1 class="game-title">EQUALCITY</h1>
  <p class="game-subtitle">Inequality &amp; Communities · Decision RPG</p>
  <div class="sdg-tagline">
    <span class="t10">SDG 10: Reduce Inequalities</span>
    <span class="sep">·</span>
    <span class="t11">SDG 11: Sustainable Cities</span>
    <span class="sep">·</span>
    <span style="color:var(--muted)">5 Levels · 5 Decisions · 1 City</span>
  </div>
  <div class="concept-cards">
    <div class="concept-card" data-num="1">
      <h3>Resource Gap</h3>
      <p>Some communities have far less access to education, healthcare, and safe housing.</p>
      <span class="sdg-tag s10">SDG 10</span>
    </div>
    <div class="concept-card" data-num="2">
      <h3>Systemic Barriers</h3>
      <p>Policies and biases can block certain groups from equal opportunities.</p>
      <span class="sdg-tag s10">SDG 10</span>
    </div>
    <div class="concept-card" data-num="3">
      <h3>Community Power</h3>
      <p>When people organise together they can demand change and lift each other up.</p>
      <span class="sdg-tag s11">SDG 11</span>
    </div>
    <div class="concept-card" data-num="4">
      <h3>Ripple Effects</h3>
      <p>One decision affects the entire community. Inequality compounds over time.</p>
      <span class="sdg-tag s10">SDG 10</span>
    </div>
    <div class="concept-card" data-num="5">
      <h3>Inclusive Cities</h3>
      <p>Sustainable cities design transport, housing and green space for everyone — not just the wealthy.</p>
      <span class="sdg-tag s11">SDG 11</spa
